# claude2026-semantic-domain.twlist
#
# Tags existing English words by professional / topical domain. Most of
# these words are already in master via kimmo (as nouns/verbs/adjectives);
# adding a domain tag means the merged type becomes much more specific
# (e.g. a grammar can ask for "a noun in the medical domain" rather than
# any noun).

